{
  "stem": "24885.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SOBBING] The war was bad, indiscriminate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the first few months, it wasn't-- for certain areas if you were able to hide out when they come to look for you, you managed to travel and get around.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then they started the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we didn't know what they were doing in the other towns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Unbeknown to us, they started to liquidate small towns into big cities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the Poles will not cooperate with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They wouldn't tell you because they are big on anti-Semitism themselves what was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were hidden for a day or two when I knew-- when the rumor was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, in those times, there lot of rumors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Tonight is going to be a big gathering and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So We were hidden out by Poles for a day or two in certain areas.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A woman on the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no-- I don't know where it originated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody came and said-- they say tonight they're going to gather up a few hundred people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hide.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If it happened or not, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With a Polish family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, in Radom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of my parents did business, some of them I knew, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we did hide.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think they knew themselves what was happening, until, for many reasons, they started-- and this started in '41-- they started hanging people for no reason at all, to scare off the rest of the population.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, the ammunition factory, which was now a town, which has been there for years-- I don't know how many thousands of people worked there, 4,000 or 5,000.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would drive us by to show us they hung 10 prominent people once a week or once a month.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
